\id JAS - Dawro 
\h Yayiqooba 
\toc3 Yay 
\toc2 Yayiqooba 
\toc1 Yayiqooba 
\mt1 Yayiqoobi 
\mt2 Xaafeedda Kiitaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Ha kiitaa xaafeedda Yayiqoobi Godaa Yesuusa ishaappe attin tammanne laa77u Yesuusa kaalliyaawanttuppe ittuwaa gidenna. Ikka Yeerusaalaamen de7iyaa ammaniyaa asaa kaalethiyaa cimaa (Gal 2:9). Ha kiitay xaafetteeddawe itti woosa gollattiw gidennaan Roome kawutethaa giddon laaletteedda Ayihuda ammaniyaawanttu ubbatuwaassa gideedda, nuunakka hachche hachche de7uwaa kaalethiyaa qofatuwaa oyqqeedda. Xaafetteeddawekka “Alamiyaa ubbaan laaletteedda Xoossaa asaassa”. Ha maxaafaa xaafeeddawe aadhdheedda eratethaa nuuni oosuwan peeshshiyaa hiillaanne ammaniyaa asaa eeshshaanne hanootaa tamaarissiyaa ogiyaa kaalesuwaa immiyaa yewatuwaa misiliyaadan qoncciyaan bessee. 
\ip Hiyyeesatethaabaa, duretethaabaa, paacciyaabaa, lo77o eeshshaabaa, qanaatiyaabaa, ammanuwaabaanne lo77o oosuwaabaa, inxxarssaa maaduwaabaanne qohuwaabaa, aadhdheedda eratethaabaa, ittuu ittuwanna walaqettiyaabaa, otoruwaabaanne ashikketethaabaa, hara asaa bolla pirddiyaawaa, ceequwaabaa woy ayyuwaabaa, genccaabaanne woosaabaa, ammaniyaa asay de7anaw bessiyaa ogiyaa ubbaa xaafeedda. 
\ip Kiitaykka kiristtinnaa de7uwan ammanuu oosuwan peeshshana hanotaabaa qonccissiide bessee. 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa 
\io1 Geluwaa (1:1) 
\io1 Ammanuwanne aadhdheedda eratethaa (1:2-8) 
\io1 Hiyyeesatethaabaanne duretethaa (1:9-11) 
\io1 Paaciyaa (1:12-18) 
\io1 Xoossaa qaalaa sisussaanne oosuwaa bolla peeshussaa (1:19-27) 
\io1 Hanenna ogiyaan ittu haraassi maaddenna mala imetteedda oduwaa (2:1-13) 
\io1 Ammanuwanne oosuwaa (2:14-26) 
\io1 Ammaniyaa asaanne inxxarssaappe kesiyaa haasayaa (3:1-18) 
\io1 Ammaniyaa asaanne ha alamiyaa (4:1-5:6) 
\io1 Dumma dumma yewuwaassi imetteedda maqquwaa (5:7-20) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Taani Yayiqoobi Xoossaa aylliinne Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa ayllii, biittaa ubbaan laaletteedda tammanne laa77u zerethatoo \f + \fr 1:1 \fq biittaa ubbaan laaletteedda tammanne laa77u zerethatoo: \ft Yayiqoobi giidde de7iyaa qofay, Godaa kaalliyaa ammaniyaawantta gidiide tammanne laa77u Isra7eeliyaa zerethatuwaadan barenttu morkketuwan biittaa ubbaa laaletti gakkeeddawantta guussaa.\f* sarotaa kiittay. 
\s1 Danddayaa, Ammanuwaa, Aadhdheedda Eratethaa 
\p  
\v 2-3 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawantto, hintte ammanuu paacettiyaawe hinttenttoo danddayaa immanaawaa eriide, dumma dumma paacii hinttena gakkiya wode, hewaa kumentha nashechchaadan paydite.  
\v 4 Hintte danddayay aynne bali baynnaan hinttena minneeddawanttanne paci bayinnawantta oothiide, bare oosuwaa polo.  
\v 5 Shin hintteppe ooninne barew aadhdheedda eratethay dhayooppe, kadhennaani ubbaw keekatethan immiya Xoossaa woosso. I aw immana.  
\v 6 Shin I ayaaninne sidhennaan ammanuwan Xoossaa woosso. Ayissi gooppe, sidhiyaa uray carkkuu sugina qaaxxiyaa abbaa beetaa mala.  
\v 7-8 Ayissi gooppe, laa77u qofay de7iya uray, bare ogiyaa ubbaan bare qofaa qachchennawe, he uray Godaappe ayinne demmanaw qoppoppo. 
\s1 Hiyyeesa Asaanne Dure Asaa Nashechchaa 
\p  
\v 9 Shin hiyyeesaa ishay Xoossay A dhoqqu ootheedda wode nashetto.  
\v 10 Qassi dure ishaykka Xoossay A kawushisseedda wode nashetto. Ayissi gooppe, dure bitani maataa giddon dicciyaa ciishshaadan dhayana. \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Isa 40:6-7\x* 
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, away bare seelaanna kesiide, maataa melissina, ciishshay dhayee; qassi A malaa lo77otethaykka dhayee; hewaadankka qassi dure bitani barewaa oothiidde dhayana. 
\s1 Asaa Bolla Gakkiya Paaciyaa 
\p  
\v 12 Waayyiyan gencciyaa uray anjjetteeddawaa; ayissi gooppe, he waayyiyaa xooneeddawaappe guyyiyan, Xoossay barena siiqiyaawanttoo immana geedda de7uwaa akililiyaa \f + \fr 1:12 \fq de7uwaa akililiyaa: \ft Bonchchetteedda de7uwaa guussaa.\f* I akkana.  
\v 13 Ooninne paacetteedda wode, “Taana Xoossay paaccee” gooppo. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay iitan paacettanaw danddayenna; qassi I bare huuphew oonanne paaccenna.  
\v 14 Shin asay huuphiyan huuphiyan bare huuphe iita amuwan gooshettiya wodenne cimettiyaa wode paacettee.  
\v 15 Hewaappe guyyiyan, amuu shahaariide, nagaraa yelee; qassi nagaray dicciide, hayquwaa yelee. 
\p  
\v 16 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, cimettoppite.  
\v 17 Lo77o imuwaa ubbayinne kumentha woytaa ubbay saluwaappe yee. Saluwaa poo7uwaa medhdheedda Aawuwaappe yee; Xoossay bare huuphew dummatennanne woy bare kuwaa laammenna.  
\v 18 Nuuni I medhdheedda medhetatuwaa giddon dhoqqasaa akkanaadan, nuuna bare sheniyaan tumu qaalaan yeleedda. 
\s1 Siseeddawaa Oosuwan Peeshshiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 19 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, hawaa hassayite; asay ubbay sisanaw elleello; shin haasayanawunne hanqqettanaw elleelloppo.  
\v 20 Ayissi gooppe, asaa hanqquu Xoossay koyyiyaa xillotethaa ahenna.  
\v 21 Hewaa diraw, tuna hanotaa ubbaanne iitatethaa ubbaa hintteppe dhayissiidde, Xoossay hintte wozanaan tookkeedda hintte shemppuwaa ashshanaw danddayiyaa qaalaa ashikketethan akkite. 
\p  
\v 22 Shin Xoossaa qaalaa oosuwan peeshshiteppe attin, sissa xalalaan hintte huuphiyaa cimmoppite.  
\v 23 Ayissi gooppe, qaalaa sisiide oothenna uray de7ooppe, I bare malaa masttootiyaa xeelliyaa uraa mala.  
\v 24 I barena xeelliide bee; ellekka I ay malenttonne dogi aggee.  
\v 25 Shin ooninne ayilletethaappe kessiyaa bali bayinna higgiyaa xeelliide, aani aqiyaawe qassi A naagiyaawe, siseeddawaakka dogennawe, he uray bare oothiyaa oosuwan anjjettana. 
\p  
\v 26 Bare inxxarssaa naagennan barena cimmiidde, barew Xoossaa goyinniyaawaa malatiyaa uray de7ooppe, A goynay mela.  
\v 27 Xoossaa Aawuwaa sinthan pokkuu bayinna geeshsha goynay hawaa; hewe haqawe gooppe, aatta aawuu bayinna naanatuwaanne waayyettiyaa am77etuwaa maaddanawaanne sa7aa nagaraa qitaappe bare huuphiyaa naaganawaa. 
\c 2  
\s1 Hiyyeesaa Kadhanaw Bessenna 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, hintte nu bonchcho Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa ammani de7iidde, deemuwaa xeelliide, asaa bonchchoppite.  
\v 2 Ayissi gooppe, worqqaa migiduwaa wothiide, lo77o mayuwaa mayyeedda itti asay hintte shiiquwaa yooppe, qassi curqqa mayuwaa mayyeedda hiyyeesaa asikka yooppe,  
\v 3 lo77o mayuwaa mayyeedda bitaniyaa hintte aathi bonchchiide A, “Neeni hawaan ubbaappe lo77iyaa oydiyan utta” giide qassi hiyyeesaa bitaniyaa, “Neeni hininna eqqashsha; woy hawaan ta gediyaa matan sa7an utta” gooppe,  
\v 4 yaatina hintte hintte giddon shaakotethaa medhdhiyaawanttanne iita qofaanna de7iyaa daannatuwaa gidikkiteeyee? 
\p  
\v 5 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, sisite; Xoossay ha sa7an de7iya hiyyeesa asay ammanuwan durettanawunne barena siiqiyaawanttoo immana geedda saluwaa kawutethaa laattanaw dooribeenneyee?  
\v 6 Shin hintte hiyyeesatuwaa toochcheeddita. Duretuu hinttena tuggayiyaawantta gidikkinooyee? Unttunttu hinttena daannan mootiyaawantta gidikkinooyee?  
\v 7 Hinttew imetteedda lo77o sunthaa boriyaawanttu unttuntta gidikkinooyee? 
\p  
\v 8 Shin Xoossaa Maxaafan, “Ne shooruwaa ne huuphiyaadan siiqa” geetettiide xaafetteedda kaatiyaa higgiyaa \f + \fr 2:8 \fq kaatiyaa higgiyaa: \ft Ubbaappe aadhuwan go77iyaa higgiyaa; hawaa bilethay, kaatiyaappe imetteeddawaa guussaa. Kaatii oonee gooppe Xoossaappe imetteedda higgiyaa.\f* hintte polooppe, lo77obaa oothiita. \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Wog 19:18\x* 
\v 9 Shin hintte asaa deemuwaa xeelliide bonchchooppe, nagaraa oothiita; qassi higgii hintte bolla, higgiyaa mentheeddawanttudan pirddana.  
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, ooninne higgiyaa ubbaa naagiide, ittinno menthiyaawaa gidooppe, he uray higgiyaa ubbaa menthee.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, “Woshummoppa” geeddawe qassi “Wodhoppa” geedda; shin neeni woshummana dhayooppekka, wodheeddawaa gidooppe, higgiyaa menthaadda. \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Kes 20:13,14; Zar 5:17,18\x* 
\v 12 Asa aylletethaappe kessiyaa higgiyan, pirddaa akkana asatuwaadan haasayitenne unttunttuwaadan oothite.  
\v 13 Ayissi gooppe, asaa maaribeenna uraa Xoossay maarennan pirddana; maarotethay pirddaa xoonee. 
\s1 Ammanuwaanne Oosuwaa 
\p  
\v 14 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, itti uray barew ammanuu de7ee gooppe, qassi A ammanuwaa A oosuu erissana dhayooppe, A ay go77anee? A ammanuu A ashshanaw danddayii?  
\v 15 Itti ishay, woy itti michchatta kallottooppe, qassi unttunttoo ubba gallassi miyaabay dhayooppe,  
\v 16 hintteppe itti uray unttuntta, “Saro biite. Tamaa ho77ite. Kalliide miite” giide, unttunttoo koshshiyaawaa immana dhayooppe, unttuntta ay go77anee?  
\v 17 Hewaa diraw, ammanuu oosuu baynnaan barekka de7ooppe hayqqeeddawaa. 
\p  
\v 18 Shin itti uray, “New ammanuu de7ee; qassi taw oosuu de7ee. Neeni ne ammanuwaa ne oosuwaappe shaakkaade taana bessa; taanikka ta ammanuwaa ta oosuwan neena bessana” gaana.  
\v 19 Neeni itti Xoossay de7iyaawaa ammanaasa; hewe lo77a. Xalahetuukka qassi ammaniino; yashshaan kokkoriino.  
\v 20 Neeni eeyay! Ammanuu oosuwaappe shaakettiide go77ennawaa \f + \fr 2:20 \fq go77ennawaa: \ft Hawaa guussay hayqqeeddawaa guussaa.\f* eranaw koyyay?  
\v 21 Nu aabbu Abraahaamo bare na7aa Yisaaqa yarshshiyaa sa7aa bolla wotheedda wode, bare oosuwan xillibeennee? \x - \xo 2:21 \xt Dom 22:1-14\x* 
\v 22 A ammanuunne A oosuu ittippe ootheeddawaanne A ammanuu A oosuwan poletteeddawaa be7ikkii?  
\v 23 Xoossaa Maxaafay “Abraahaamo Xoossaa ammaneedda. Xoossaykka hewaa aw xillotethan paydeedda” geeddawe poletteedda; qassi Xoossaa dabbo geetettiide I xeesetteedda. \x - \xo 2:23 \xt Dom 15:6; 2Od 20:7; Isa 41:8\x* 
\v 24 Asay ammano xalalaana gidennaan, oosuwan xilliyaawaa hintte be7iita. 
\p  
\v 25 Hewaadankka qassi caaratta Ra7aaba kiitettowantta mokkaade hara ogiyaanna unttuntta moyizzeedda wode, bare oosuwan xillabeykkee? \x - \xo 2:25 \xt Iya 2:1-21\x* 
\p  
\v 26 Ayissi gooppe, shemppuu shaaketteedda bollay hayiqqeeddawaa gidiyaawaadan, hewaadankka qassi oosuu shaaketteedda ammanuu hayqqeeddawaa. 
\c 3  
\s1 Inxxarssaa Naagiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, nuuni haratuwaappe aadhdhiyaa pirddaa akkanawaa hintte eriya diraw, hintteppe coratuu tamaarissiyaawantta gidoppite.  
\v 2 Nuuni ubbayikka daroban baleetto; itti uray bare haasayan mulekka balana dhayooppe, I barena naaganaw danddayiyaa bali bayinna asaa.  
\v 3 Paratuu nuussi azazettana mala, bixaalaa barssiide, nuuni koyyiyaasaa ubbaa unttuntta afeetto.  
\v 4 Be7ite, markkabetuukka qassi hewaa keenaa wolqqaama gidiidde, gotuwaa carkkuwan laagettoopekka, unttuntta laaggiyaawe barewaa koyyiyaasaa zaariide laaggiyaa qeeri guuthaa mithaan laagettiide biino.  
\v 5 Hewaadan inxxarssay bollaa giddon guutha asatethaa gidooppekka, daro wolqqaamaban ceeqettee. 
\p Guutha tamay waaniide wolqqaama woraa guuddii! Akeekite.  
\v 6 Inxxarssaykka tamaa mala. I nu asatethaa giddon iitabaa ubbaa oothana danddayee; asatethaa ubbaa tunissee. Qassi nu de7uwaa wothaakka tamaan guuddee; Gaannamiyaa tamaan I guudettanawaa.  
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, do7atuwaa, kafatuwaa zariyaa, tiraan gooshettiya shooshshatuu zariyaanne abbaan de7iya medhetatuwaa zariyaa ubbaa asay aadisseedda; qassi unttunttukka aadeeddino.  
\v 8 Shin ooninne inxxarssaa aadissanaw danddayibeenna; inxxarssay wodhiyaa marzzii kumeedda co77u geenna iita medhetaa.  
\v 9 Nuuni inxxarssan nu Godaanne Aawuwaa galateetto; qassi aanikka Xoossaa malatiide medhetteedda asaa sheqqeetto. \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Dom 1:26\x* 
\v 10 Itti doonaappe galataynne sheqay kesee. Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, hewe hewaadan hananaw bessenna.  
\v 11 Pulttuu itti ollaappe mal77iyaa haathaanne cammiyaa haathaa pulttanaw danddayii?  
\v 12 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, balasiyaa giya mithay wogaraa ayifanaw danddayii? Woy woyiniyaa turay balasiyaa giya mithaa ayifanaw danddayii? Maxine maxine giya haathaappekka mal77o haathay kesana danddayenna. 
\s1 Saluwaa Aadhdheedda Eraanne Sa7aa Aadhdheedda Eraa 
\p  
\v 13 Hintte giddon aadhdheedda eranchchayinne akeekanchchay oonee? Bare lo77o de7uwan oosetteedda bare oosuwaa aadhdheedda eratethaappe yiyaa ashikketethaan besso.  
\v 14 Shin hintte wozanaan cammiyaa qanaatiinne yirggii de7oppo. Qassi tumatethaa bollaakka worddotoppitenne otorettoppite.  
\v 15 Hewaa mala aadhdheedda eratethay saluwaappe wodhdhiyaawaa gidenna; shin hewe sa7aabaa, asaawaa, xalahatuwawaa.  
\v 16 Ayissi gooppe, qanaatiinne yirggii de7iyaasaan walassayinne iita ooso ubbay de7ee.  
\v 17 Shin bollappe yiyaa aadhdheedda eratethay ubbaappe kase geeshsha. Qassi sarotethaa dosiyaawaa, ashikkenne eeno giyaawaa; qassi maarotethaynne lo77o ayfii kumeeddawaa. Sidhiinne lo77o malatiyaa iitatethay bayinnawaa.  
\v 18 Xillotethaa ayfii sarotethaa oothiyaawanttu sarotethaan zereedda zerethaappe beetteedda. 
\c 4  
\s1 Ha Alamiyaa Iitatethaa Dosennan Agganawaa 
\p  
\v 1 Olaynne walassay hintte gidduwaa haqappe yii? Unttunttu yedasay hintte bollaa giddon olettiyaa hintte nashettanaw wolqqaama amuwaa amottiyaawaappe gidennee?  
\v 2 Hintte amottiita; shin demmikkita; wodhiita. Loythi koyyiita; shin demmanaw danddayikkita; walaqqetiitanne olettiita. Shin Xoossaa woossenna diraw, hintte koyiyaawaa demmikkita.  
\v 3 Xoossaa woossiita, shin demmikkita; gaasuukka balaa ogiyaan woossiita. Hewaa hinttena nashechchiyaawaan peeshshanaw koyyiyaa diraassa.  
\v 4 Simmi woshummiyaawanttoo, ha alamiyaanna dabbotiyaawe Xoossaw morkke gidiyaawaa erikkitee? Ayissi gooppe, ha alamiyaanna dabbotanaw koyyiyaawe ooninne Xoossaanna morkkettee.  
\v 5 Woy Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Xoossay nuunan wotheedda Ayyaanay wolqqaama amuwaa nuussi amottee” \f + \fr 4:5 \fq “Xoossay nuunan wotheedda Ayyaanay wolqqaama amuwaa amottee”: \ft Xoossay nuunan bare Ayyaanaa wotheeddawe, nuussi lo77o qofaa amottiyaawaana.\f* giyaawaa hinttenttoo coo giyaawaa malatii?  
\v 6 Shin Xoossay aadho keekatethaa aathiide immee. Hewaa diraw, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Xoossay otorettiyaawantta ixxee; shin barena kawushshiyaawanttoo aadho keekatethaa immee” yaage. \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Lem 3:34\x* 
\p  
\v 7 Simmi, hintte Xoossaw moodettite. Yaatiide xalahiyaanna eqettite; I hintteppe baqatana.  
\v 8 Xoossaakko shiiqite; ikka hinttekko shiiqana. Hinttenoo nagaranchchatoo, hintte kushiyaa meecettite. Laa77u qofay de7iyaawanttoo, hintte wozanaa geeshshite.  
\v 9 Tuggattite; kayyottitenne yeekkite. Hintte miichchaa yeekoo laammite; hintte nashechchaakka kayyoo laammite.  
\v 10 Godaa sinthan hintte huuphiyaa toochchite; qassi I hinttena dhoqqu dhoqqu oothana. 
\s1 Asaa Bolla Pirddennaan Agganawaa 
\p  
\v 11 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, ittuu ittuwaa zigiroppite. Bare ishaa zigiriyaawenne A bolla pirddiyaawe higgiyaa zigireenne higgiyaa bolla pirddee. Neeni higgiyaa bolla pirddooppe, higgiyaa bolla pirddiyaawaa gidaasappe attin, higgew azazettiyaawaa gidakka.  
\v 12 Higgiyaa immiyaawenne pirddiyaawe Xoossaa xalalaa; I ashshanawunne dhayissanaw danddayee; shin ne shooruwaa bolla pirddiyaawe neeni oonee? 
\s1 Ceeqettennaadan Imetteedda Zoriyaa 
\p  
\v 13 Hinttenoo, “Nuuni hachche woy wontti he katamaa baana; hewan laythaa uttana; zali77ananne qassi miishshaa wodhissana” giyaawanttoo, be7ite. \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Lem 27:1\x* 
\v 14 Wontti hintte de7uu ayaa hananenttonne erikkita; guutha wodew hintte beettiide, guyyeppe dhayiyaa peenuwa mala.  
\v 15 Hewaa aggiide, “Goday gooppe, nuuni de7ana; hawaa woy hewaa oothana” gaanaw bessee.  
\v 16 Shin hintte ha77i hinttenttu dhoqqatethaan ceeqettiita; hewaa mala ceequu ubbay iita. 
\p  
\v 17 Hewaa diraw, lo77obaa oothanaw eriidde oothenna uraw hewe nagaraa. 
\c 5  
\s1 Dure Asaassi Imetteedda Mino Zoriyaa 
\p  
\v 1 Ha77ikka hinttenoo dure asatoo, hintte bolla yiyaa tuggaw “Aayyee! Aayyee!” yaagiide yeekkitenne zilalite.  
\v 2 Hintte duretethay baydiggeedda; qassi hintte afilaakka bil77ay midiggeedda.  
\v 3 Hintte worqqaynne hintte biray shi7i diggeedda. Qassi he shi7ay hintte bolla markkattana; hintte bollaakka tamaadan maana. Hintte hintte miishshaa sinthaw dagay de7iita.  
\v 4 Akeekite; hintte gaden kathaa qoyceedda asatoo ciggibeenna kiraa miishshay waassee; unttunttu waasuu wolqqaama Godaa hayithan sisetteedda. \x - \xo 5:4 \xt Zar 24:14-15\x* 
\v 5 Hinttew injjetina, sa7an ishaliide de7eeddita; shukaa gallassaw dhiikkiyaawaadan, hintte bollaa dhiikkeeddita.  
\v 6 Xillo asaa bolla pirddeeddita; qassi A wodheeddita; I hinttenanna eqettenna. 
\s1 Godaa laa7entho Yuussaa Danddayan Naagiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, Goday yaana gakkanaw genccite; biittaa goshiyaawe adilliyaa iraynne assuuraa iray yaana gakkanaw gencciide, al77o kathaa I wooti naagiide gathi akkintto be7ite.  
\v 8 Hinttekka qassi genccite; hintte wozanaa minissite. Ayissi gooppe, Godaa yuussay matatteedda. 
\p  
\v 9 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, Xoossay hintte bolla pirddenna mala, ittuu ittuwaa bolla zuuzummoppite. Be7ite, pirddiyaawe penggiyan eqqeedda.  
\v 10 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, waayyiyaassinne genccaassi leemisuwaa gideeddawantta, Godaa sunthan haasayeedda nabatuwaa hassayite.  
\v 11 Be7ite, danddayiide gencceeddawantta nuuni anjjetteeddawantta geetto. Iyyooba genccaa hintte siseeddita; qassi Goday aw wurssethaan immeeddawaakka be7eeddita. Ayissi gooppe, Goday maarotaynne qaretay kumeeddawaa. \x - \xo 5:11 \xt Yob 1:21-22; 2:10; Maz 103:8\x* 
\p  
\v 12 Shin ubbaappe kase, taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, saluwan gidina, woy sa7an gidina, woy hara caaquwaan gidina, ayankka caaqqoppite. Shin Xoossaa pirddan hintte gelennaadan, hintte yewuu E giyaawaa gidooppe, “E” giite; gidenna giyaawaa gidooppe, “Gidenna” giite. 
\p  
\v 13 Hintte giddon waayyettiyaa uray ooninne de7ooppe, Xoossaa woosso; nashettiyaa uray ooninne de7ooppe, yexxiide galato.  
\v 14 Hintteppe sakettiyaa uray ooninne de7ooppe, ammaniyaa asaa kaalethiyaa cimatuwaa barekko xeeso; unttunttu Godaa sunthan zaytiyaa A okkiide, aw Xoossaa woossino.  
\v 15 Ammanuwan Xoossaa woosseedda woosay hargganchchaa pathana; Godaykka A harggiyaappe denthana; qassi nagaraa I ootheeddawaa gidooppekka Goday aw atto gaana.  
\v 16 Hewaa diraw, hintte paxana mala, hintte nagaraa ittuu ittoo paaxitenne ittuu ittoo Xoossaa woossite; xillo asaa woosay wolqqaama oosuwaa oothee.  
\v 17 Eelaas nu mala asaa. Iray sa7an bukkennaadan, I minissiide, Xoossaa woossina heezzu laythanne usuppun agenaa sa7an iray bukkibeenna. \x - \xo 5:17 \xt 1Ka 17:1; 18:1\x* 
\v 18 Laa7enthuwaa Xoossaa I woossina, saluwaappe iray bukkeedda; sa7aykka bare kathaa mokkeedda. \x - \xo 5:18 \xt 1Ka 18:42-45\x* 
\p  
\v 19 Taanaadan Xoossaa kaalliyaawanttoo, hintteppe ooninne tumuwaappe wora booppe, qassi ittuu A guyye he tumuwaakko zaarooppe,  
\v 20 nagaranchchaa A balaa ogiyaappe zaariyaa ooninne A shemppuwaa hayiquwaappe ashshanawaanne daro nagaraa kammanawaa ero. \x - \xo 5:20 \xt Lem 10:12; 1Ph 4:8\x*